ges/v5wcf99jssujDm04ZqBqt.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/tPTAOM6qK9lApBYm91P3x.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/e9heEehMBd0KisqCJ7uGH.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WwUgKIncRxVn9xqiuQoOS.jpg?height=144&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/giPqkfavbHRVAjG6SaCvJ.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9FFeqeYeBf70-c7-eBNjO.jpg?height=442&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fE3ORwToZq7_9BQlZXXYP.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/llzbFylmztzp4qf1mrG_W.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/fKdeLD30CU8uDVauiEGzZ.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/mMPm1F097k6CU8y-_LS2c.jpg?height=442&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Sjs62fMsZK6M5NNZJ5iCq.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/hBFpkUsNxtLyVRkcUoF4C.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ypuYzl-2CnDXetBCoQGU9.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/iu2WPrnAiRpcXsPZhqfQf.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ulR_vDmCZnl8jKi9nF-sy.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JByjBXbMHT1N_v9IeE3We.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FOBaAdYvZ85-bEOlNJkPO.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/AJlrF-WvylFjJB6dBgOew.jpg?height=442&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2IXbmihgT1szPvG5EeF06.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/PtHbJRFRgIuWI6ih9R71c.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/mm0WGRZCHN9lTriZKBxTD.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/p6aXQgTyTtMYcnWyfaKPp.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WE74wNPTVQup6Hpv1JTQh.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WhYlDx_rKS0PoT96d_inG.jpg?height=144&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rI93EW_jubL_QIBunTQNT.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/aYJbLeH-zXgQAjw8Kv2WO.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5LHxgtHncbsCYqJkBiJeB.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_PRP05N27FI-Q5EfyG1zL.jpg?height=144&width=1080)\\n\\n柳暗花明，绝处逢生；多年隐忍，一战成名。\\n\\n \\n \\n\\nTwitter和Zynga代表了USV的高光时刻，也是创业无常的代表符号。\\n\\n \\n \\n\\nTwitter和Zynga创始于偶然，成长于必然；起伏于哗然，回归于自然，波澜壮阔又云淡风轻。\\n\\n \\n \\n\\n下周四，我们将放送《USV投资解构：柴米油盐（下）》，对USV的另外两个投资案例Lending Club和Edmodo进行详细解构，看看USV如何通过严格的退出原则和管理，深度挖掘一支VC基金95%的中等项目的潜在价值，化平淡为神奇。\\n\\n \\n \\n\\n敬请期待！\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nEGT9FIb0ZS78qt2mH5Xo.jpg?height=144&width=1080)\\n\\n**往期回顾**\\n\\n\\\\-点击下图浏览-\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/UY3VlK8lzZFPLvDfJCMM-.png?height=735&width=901)\\n\\n[链接](https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XF5k1BraHW0VLSmVISRTHA)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8btX2dddUXR7TS4ddgJTE.jpg?height=810&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/bIDAcH4j4al7ilz9iwpHv.png?height=818&width=996)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640850307,\"title\":\"USV四部曲之二丨百亿美金社交游戏独角兽的培养基\"},\"digest\":\"MYlk7_AFj5jB20tMP5HmqPMdGqy5y9iDYodshf-jjCM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8a8b0bf39